column5: Well, it might be -1 degrees C here, but don't be fooled, the ticks are out in force this year. Have peeled around six off myself in the last week and pulled another 2 off the poor dog tonight ..gross! Bring some tweezers up with you this year if you are coming to Northwest Ontario.TICK VIDEOhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=och-T6bFua8
bring a repelant that has 98% deet, and you will not have a problem
